===Suffix===
'''-sam'''
# [[denote|Denote]]s an [[adjective]] or an [[adverb]]. [[often|Often]] [[one]] [[word]] [[means]] [[both]] [[depending]] on the [[context]] (e.g. ''[[langsam]]'' [[can]] mean [[either]] ''[[slow]]'' or ''[[slowly]]''; ''[[aufmerksam]]'' can mean ''[[intent]]'' but it can also mean ''[[intently]]'').

